Connections

Bluetooth Module:
VCC → Arduino 5V
GND → Arduino GND
TXD → Arduino RX (Pin 0)
RXD → Arduino TX (Pin 1)

LED:
Positive leg (anode) → Arduino Pin 13 (via a resistor)
Negative leg (cathode) → Arduino GND


Ensure the Bluetooth module is paired with your phone using a Bluetooth control app.

